com.orchestranetworks.service
Class ArchiveImportSpec

java.lang.Object
  com.orchestranetworks.service.ArchiveImportSpec
public class ArchiveImportSpec
extends Object

Defines the settings of an archive import.

To be valid, an instance of this class must at least define an archive source. If no data sets are specified, then all the archive content will be imported.

See Also:
ProcedureContext.doImportArchive(ArchiveImportSpec)
